<h1><a href="http://thinkprogress.org/justice/2014/02/03/3242381/republicans-trick-voters-donating-democratic-candidates/">Trick Websites Dupe Democrats Into Donating To Republicans</a></h1>

<div class="post">

<p class="timestamp">
	<span class="byline"> by Rebecca Leber </span><span class="posted-on">Posted on <time class="published" datetime="February 3, 2014 at 5:17 pm">February 3, 2014 at 5:17 pm</time>&nbsp;<time class="updated" datetime="February 22, 2014 at 10:10 am">Updated: February 22, 2014 at 10:10 am</time></span></p>


